{"tid":1285114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"縱卡夫卡再生，也寫不出香港6月的荒謬⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T01:37:47.000Z","uid":266121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"385e0e2ddccaab087c0ef24b688ee370032f6557","tid":1285114,"uid":266121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"這二十二年之荒謬絕倫，縱使卡夫卡在世且生活在香港，也寫不出這樣的劇本。香港以法制、自由以及高素質的公民社會聞名世界，然而，當7月1日，一群絕望的香港年輕人，終於占領了本屬於為人民代言的立法會時，這也無疑是世界上最大的魔幻現實諷刺劇。一個標榜為人民立法的地方，竟然被人民所占領，而且不是少數，是代表了幾百萬香港人的多數群體。卡夫卡可以想到有這樣荒唐的情節麼？這過去的22年，這個立法會是在怎樣「合理」的外觀之下，將香港變得越來越卡夫卡式的魔幻？以至於年輕人終於怒吼上街！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%E5%A4%AB%E5%8D%A1-3ad7f440867a?source=friends_link&amp;sk=cef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fmount-davis%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%258D%25A1-3ad7f440867a%3Fsource%3Dfriends_link%26sk%3Dcef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24%C5%92LIHKG%C5%92&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=b457ab4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%E5%A4%AB%E5%8D%A1-3ad7f440867a?source=friends_link&amp;sk=cef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24</a><a href=\"https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%E5%A4%AB%E5%8D%A1-3ad7f440867a?source=friends_link&amp;sk=cef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fmount-davis%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%258D%25A1-3ad7f440867a%3Fsource%3Dfriends_link%26sk%3Dcef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=acf96723\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/mount-davis/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%E5%A4%AB%E5%8D%A1-3ad7f440867a?source=friends_link&amp;sk=cef9e28831825819eb221245ed25ba24</a>"},{"pid":"4a3